{"tid":869884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本跨黨派議員參拜靖國神社 18/10","createTime":"2018-10-20T15:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T06:20:58.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"744a6d3bf627004c6725a8f066bd9ab35a7361a4","tid":869884,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"日本跨黨派議員參拜靖國神社 18/10<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00005/1539851256942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00005%2F1539851256942&d=nhvwAzsgV8qdFi8eY%2FQ2XQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=542da3df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00005%2F1539851256942&h=32fd7c08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00005/1539851256942</a><br />\n<br />\n日本71名跨黨派國會議員組成聯盟，今早在秋祭期間，參拜靖國神社。其中包括首相安倍晉三7名內閣成員：特別顧問衛藤晟一及農業部長高鳥修一等。安倍晉三則正訪問歐洲，沒有前往神社參拜，但昨日以內閣總理大臣身分，奉獻名為「真榊」的祭品。<br />\n<br />\n該議員聯盟每逢4月春季例行大祭、10月秋季例行大祭，及8月15日的日本戰敗投降日，都會參拜靖國神社。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於安倍晉三向靖國神社奉獻祭品，中國外交部發言人陸慷在昨日的例行記者會上指出，靖國神社供奉着對侵略戰爭負有直接責任的二戰甲級戰犯，中方一貫反對日方的錯誤做法，又敦促日方切實正視和深刻反省侵略歷史，以實際行動取信於亞洲鄰國和國際社會。</span><br />\n<br />\n(日本放送協會/共同社/人民網/多維新聞)"},{"pid":"7a644ac1f62b5c03f3b33b1fa0875c3b24d468ea","tid":869884,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7628dc25eb4b5e76ccd48d8af960688b01344252","tid":869884,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"係時候清一清班垃圾"},{"pid":"d17e21cd33e9ae4f0329bd651ac94db486e596a4","tid":869884,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lo